          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1654600748965-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>sauce has thickened, remove the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>beans</strong> from the heat, squeeze in the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and mix everything together</p><p>Gently crush some of the beans lightly with a masher and season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – these are your <strong>Mexican-style beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1654600751219-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1654600751219-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1654600751219-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1654600751219-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1654600751219-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Crack your <strong>egg[s] </strong>into the pan</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p><p>Tip: Give your eggs a little shake before you crack them for perfectly centred yolks!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1654600753558-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1654600753558-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1654600753558-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1654600753558-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1654600753558-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Serve the<strong> Mexican-style beans</strong> over the <strong>warmed tortillas </strong>and top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and a<strong> fried egg</strong> – this is your <strong>huevos rancheros</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the<strong> coriander oil</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
